Two grand.

53
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,629
Hold on.

54
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,919
Hallelujah.

55
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:22,913
You're my savior.
My own personal Jesus Christ.

56
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,957
You get caught using that....

57
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:27,236
I know. This never happened.
You don't exist.

58
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:30,311
-Right.
-Something wrong, man?

59
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,516
You look a little whiter than usual.

60
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:35,670
My computer, it....

61
00:08:38,560 --> 00:08:42,917
Ever have that feeling where you're
not sure if you're awake or dreaming?

62
00:08:43,680 --> 00:08:46,319
All the time.
It's called mescaline.

63
