How did you do that?

85
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:20,154
Right now, all I can tell you...

86
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,239
...is that you're in danger.

87
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:24,989
-I brought you here to warn you.
