90
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,152
I know why you're here, Neo.

91
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:37,797
I know what you've been doing.

92
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,837
I know why you hardly sleep...

93
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:43,112
...why you live alone and why,
night after night...

94
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,590
...you sit at your computer.

95
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,199
You're looking for him.

96
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:51,838
I know, because I was once
looking for the same thing.

97
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:54,356
And when he found me...

98
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:57,918
...he told me I wasn't really
looking for him...

99
00:10:58,800 --> 00:11:00,472
...I was looking for an answer.

100
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:04,072
It's the question that drives us, Neo.

101
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:07,280
It's the question
that brought you here.

102
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,599
You know the question...

103
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,273
...just as I did.

104
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:15,318
What is the Matrix?

105
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:17,915
The answer is out there, Neo.

106
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:20,471
It's looking for you.

107
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,878
And it will find you...

108
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,031
...if you want it to.

109
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:32,549
Shit.

110
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,789
Shit, shit.

111
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:46,359
You have a problem with authority,
Mr. Anderson.

112
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:50,479
You believe that you are special,
that the rules do not apply to you.

113
