121
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,389
Yes, Mr. Rhineheart.
Perfectly clear.

122
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:34,431
Thomas Anderson?

123
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,873
Yeah, that's me.

124
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:45,675
Great.

125
00:12:47,040 --> 00:12:48,155
Have a nice day.

126
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:07,477
Hello, Neo. Do you know who this is?

127
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:11,312
-Morpheus.
- Yes.

128
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:13,471
I've been looking for you.

129
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:16,757
I don 't know if you 're ready to see
what I want to show you.

130
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:20,037
But unfortunately, you and I
have run out of time.

131
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:23,829
They're coming for you, and I don 't know
what they're going to do.

132
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,354
Who's coming for me?

133
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:27,591
Stand up and see for yourself.

134
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:30,513
-What? Right now?
- Yes.

135
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:31,954
Now.

136
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:34,597
